Package it.cnr.isti.thematrix.mapping.creator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IadCreator
    Class to execute queries on the DBMS and retrieve datasets, called by MappingManager.
    MySQLAccess
    Class holding code to access MySQL database in streaming fashion, version one.
    QueryCreator
    This class generates the test of SQL queries needed to extract a IAD dataset file from a DBMS.
    ValueRemapper
    THis class should translate the header names and values retrieved from DB (LIAD) into values suitable for the CSV file cache (IAD).
